      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's good to hear. My partner is a bit of a perfectionist with these things, though. He was actually looking at some of the sensor data from the smart home system during the walkthrough and mentioned noticing a slight reading irregularity near the foundation area. Could you check the most recent technical logs just to make sure nothing was missed in the standard inspection?",
